瓶</a>。</p><p>格拉斯顿伯里音乐节于 6 月 26 日至 30 日举行，由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">Coldplay</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a>领衔。参加今年音乐节的其他乐队包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shania-twain">Shania Twain</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lcd-soundsystem">LCD Soundsystem</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">Little Simz</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">The National</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/avril-lavigne">Avril Lavigne</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sugababes">Sugababes</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jungle">Jungle</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/idles">IDLES</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justice">Justice</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bloc-party">Bloc Party</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yard-act">Yard Act</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arlo-parks">Arlo Parks</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gossip">Gossip</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/emily-eavis-reports-glastonbury-attendees-have-taken-99-per-cent-of-tents-home-with-them-3771879">Emily Eavis 报道格拉斯顿伯里音乐节与会者已将 99% 的帐篷带回家，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
